1
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:44,300
"Unfold"

2
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,500
(Episode 5)

3
00:02:01,458 --> 00:02:02,458
I looked into it.

4
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:04,250
There are no leads.

5
00:02:04,666 --> 00:02:06,458
So, did I kill him in my sleep?

6
00:02:08,125 --> 00:02:08,958
Did you find out

7
00:02:08,958 --> 00:02:10,208
who he met that day?

8
00:02:11,041 --> 00:02:12,041
Yes.

9
00:02:12,333 --> 00:02:13,333
His adopted son.

10
00:02:16,083 --> 00:02:17,458
The one who cleans up dead bodies.

11
00:02:18,125 --> 00:02:19,208
What motive could he have?

12
00:02:21,125 --> 00:02:22,125
I don't know.

13
00:02:22,333 --> 00:02:23,500
But...

14
00:02:24,208 --> 00:02:26,333
he was the last person to see Lao Bai alive.

15
00:02:27,083 --> 00:02:28,750
And it was at the place he was cleaning.

16
00:02:32,833 --> 00:02:34,166
Are you saying

17
00:02:34,166 --> 00:02:35,583
he killed his own father

18
00:02:35,958 --> 00:02:37,166
at his workplace,

19
00:02:37,375 --> 00:02:38,541
and then called the police himself?

20
00:03:32,375 --> 00:03:33,375
What are you waiting for?

21
00:03:33,916 --> 00:03:34,916
Hurry up.

22
00:03:44,791 --> 00:03:45,666
Look,

23
00:03:45,791 --> 00:03:47,541
the assistant you asked for last time,

24
00:03:47,791 --> 00:03:49,750
I brought him to you today.

25
00:03:50,333 --> 00:03:52,500
From now on, any dirty or heavy work,

26
00:03:53,166 --> 00:03:54,166
just leave it to him.

27
00:04:19,833 --> 00:04:20,875
Do you know

28
00:04:22,041 --> 00:04:23,791
what kind of work you're here to do?

29
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:28,250
Yes.

30
00:04:29,208 --> 00:04:30,291
Uncle Bai told me.

31
00:04:41,291 --> 00:04:42,666
Do you know what the job entails?

32
00:04:44,916 --> 00:04:45,916
He told me.

33
00:05:12,833 --> 00:05:14,333
You'll be staying in this room from now on.

34
00:05:16,125 --> 00:05:17,125
Go upstairs and take a shower.

35
00:05:17,291 --> 00:05:18,291
Do I need to ask you twice?

36
00:06:10,333 --> 00:06:11,333
Get up already.

37
00:06:29,916 --> 00:06:31,000
You're so warm.

38
00:08:11,791 --> 00:08:13,041
Do you know that adopted son?

39
00:08:14,583 --> 00:08:16,000
I only know what he looks like,

40
00:08:16,708 --> 00:08:17,708
but I don't know him personally.

41
00:08:18,958 --> 00:08:20,250
After Bai Ronghui died,

42
00:08:20,791 --> 00:08:22,583
my uncles started making trouble.

43
00:08:23,458 --> 00:08:24,833
I had my lawyer look into it.

44
00:08:26,083 --> 00:08:27,708
That adopted son inherited

45
00:08:27,791 --> 00:08:28,916
his shares in the port.

46
00:08:29,875 --> 00:08:31,250
I want you to make him sell them to me.

47
00:08:32,458 --> 00:08:33,333
We must take the initiative

48
00:08:33,333 --> 00:08:34,875
and keep control in our own hands.

49
00:08:36,583 --> 00:08:37,583
Also,

50
00:08:39,666 --> 00:08:40,958
you mentioned earlier

51
00:08:41,208 --> 00:08:42,791
that Bai Che killed the old man.

52
00:08:43,375 --> 00:08:44,708
That's not entirely impossible.

53
00:08:47,416 --> 00:08:48,416
Look at this.

54
00:09:46,125 --> 00:09:47,916
I've transferred 20,000 yuan to you.

55
00:09:48,541 --> 00:09:50,583
You're only sixteen,

56
00:09:50,916 --> 00:09:52,291
yet you can make this much money.

57
00:09:52,583 --> 00:09:54,208
You can spend it however you want.

58
00:09:55,083 --> 00:09:56,541
If I were you,

59
00:09:56,541 --> 00:09:57,750
I'd drop out of school

60
00:09:58,333 --> 00:09:59,458
and do this full-time

61
00:10:00,083 --> 00:10:01,291
to make even more money.

62
00:10:41,125 --> 00:10:43,000
Fortunately, most of the orders are normal.

63
00:10:58,041 --> 00:10:59,041
Cheng Fan.

64
00:11:34,708 --> 00:11:36,750
Sorry, we're closed.

65
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:39,875
You're Bai Che, right?

66
00:11:41,250 --> 00:11:42,250
Yes.

67
00:11:42,875 --> 00:11:44,083
And you are?

68
00:11:44,833 --> 00:11:46,000
Who I am doesn't matter.

69
00:11:46,916 --> 00:11:48,375
You're Bai Ronghui's son, right?

70
00:11:51,958 --> 00:11:53,166
Are you looking for him?

71
00:11:53,791 --> 00:11:54,958
I know he's dead.

72
00:11:56,125 --> 00:11:57,416
I'm here for you.

73
00:12:01,041 --> 00:12:02,458
I won't beat around the bush.

74
00:12:04,791 --> 00:12:05,541
Bai Ronghui used to run

75
00:12:05,541 --> 00:12:07,125
a lot of shady businesses.

76
00:12:07,291 --> 00:12:08,291
You knew that, right?

77
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:10,500
After his death,

78
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,125
his shares in a port

79
00:12:12,666 --> 00:12:13,750
passed on to you.

80
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,000
I want you to sell them to me.

81
00:12:16,875 --> 00:12:17,958
What port?

82
00:12:18,958 --> 00:12:20,416
I don't know what you're talking about.

83
00:12:26,208 --> 00:12:27,208
First,

84
00:12:27,375 --> 00:12:28,708
I told you I don't waste words.

85
00:12:29,583 --> 00:12:30,583
Second,

86
00:12:31,166 --> 00:12:32,291
I'm here to notify you,

87
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,291
not to negotiate.

88
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,250
Who are you to my dad?

89
00:12:39,291 --> 00:12:40,916
Calling him "dad"...

90
00:12:41,916 --> 00:12:43,083
It seems you two

91
00:12:43,083 --> 00:12:44,375
had a good relationship.

92
00:12:46,458 --> 00:12:47,458
But did you know?

93
00:12:48,208 --> 00:12:49,208
Your last name, Bai,

94
00:12:51,083 --> 00:12:52,625
doesn't come from Bai Ronghui.

95
00:12:54,708 --> 00:12:55,708
What do you mean?

96
00:12:58,583 --> 00:12:59,833
Do you know how your dad

97
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:01,541
got his hands on you?

98
00:13:04,708 --> 00:13:05,708
Open it.

99
00:13:21,394 --> 00:13:24,094
[Married National Enterprise Couple Seek Lost Child]

100
00:13:24,574 --> 00:13:27,687
[Missing Person]

101
00:13:35,714 --> 00:13:38,514
[TN: Educated guess that this is a police
report from "Mo Ziqiang" for the child-napping.]

102
00:13:51,458 --> 00:13:53,500
You weren't adopted from an orphanage.

103
00:13:54,708 --> 00:13:55,916
Your so-called father

104
00:13:56,291 --> 00:13:57,541
is the one who abducted you.

105
00:13:59,125 --> 00:14:00,125
You're lying!

106
00:14:01,625 --> 00:14:02,750
These news reports...

107
00:14:02,833 --> 00:14:04,500
You can look them up yourself.

108
00:14:06,458 --> 00:14:08,333
You have no real connection to Bai Ronghui.

109
00:14:08,583 --> 00:14:10,083
You were just a pawn to him.

110
00:14:11,666 --> 00:14:12,708
Sell the port,

111
00:14:13,166 --> 00:14:14,416
and get out of this city.

112
00:14:16,875 --> 00:14:17,875
Here's my card.

113
00:14:18,458 --> 00:14:19,458
Make up your mind quickly.

114
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:20,625
I'll be back every day.

115
00:14:41,333 --> 00:14:42,333
Bai Che,

116
00:14:47,583 --> 00:14:48,791
I killed your father.
